<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>클라이언트-서버 인터랙션 데모</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>클라이언트-서버 요청 실습</h1>

  <h2>1. GET 요청 (검색)</h2>
  <form action="/search" method="get">
    <p>값 1:<input type="text" name="v1" placeholder="입력"></p>
    <p>값 2:<input type="text" name="v2" placeholder="입력"></p>
    <button>제출</button>
  </form>

  <h2>2. POST 요청 (댓글 작성)</h2>
  <form action="/submit" method="post">
    <p>값 1:<input type="text" name="t1" placeholder="입력"></p>
    <p>값 2:<input type="text" name="t2" placeholder="입력"></p>
    <button>POST 요청 보내기</button>
  </form>
</body>
</html>
